<p style="font-size:16px; font-family:Courier New">

		This is to inform everyone that two (2) of our PLDT Fibr Internet lines are down (LOS). As such, everyone is advised to turn-off video streaming (netflix, hbo etc), music streaming (spotify, youtube music etc), online games and other internet-hungry applications for desktop, laptop, mobile phones, tablets, in order to conserve and share internet bandwith.

</p>
<p style="font-size:16px;font-family:Courier New>
	Responsible use of internet resource is encouraged. Please be guided accordingly.

</p>